{"id": 562, "genre": 1001, "title": "你有过哪些选择恐惧症？", "description": "最后发现是我想太多。", "record_count": 8490, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194326Rp0Wz8cNenuismDj.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-09T11:13:14Z", "options": [{"id": 15872, "content": "选择什么输入法，什么浏览器，什么新闻客户端", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139135}, {"id": 16129, "content": "我做什么事都有选择恐惧症，结婚，找一个爱我的人，还是这个条件好的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241246}, {"id": 16130, "content": "方法", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241246}, {"id": 16642, "content": "冬天晚上睡觉前到底要不要去上个厕所", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248188}, {"id": 18178, "content": "所有的选择恐惧症，都是，qiong，穷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256506}, {"id": 15876, "content": "有钱就都买咯", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234356}, {"id": 18948, "content": "车位太多了不知道选哪个，纠结！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257097}, {"id": 16645, "content": "买洗衣液or洗衣粉？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248261}, {"id": 15878, "content": "三长一短该选谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232230}, {"id": 15880, "content": "好害怕被甩???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238157}, {"id": 17160, "content": "主要是胖 才有选择困难症", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250080}, {"id": 44041, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440413}, {"id": 15882, "content": "无女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238172}, {"id": 15883, "content": "都是因为没钱和胖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238166}, {"id": 15886, "content": "要不要打开对话框", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222933}, {"id": 15888, "content": "我到底要吃啥，去哪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109333}, {"id": 15889, "content": "发照片的时候好几种滤镜都好看 都有不同感觉 不知道选哪个", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211155MyJlORpw8NKLcIV6.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227722}, {"id": 16145, "content": "问对方想吃什么 确回答随便", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241510}, {"id": 18961, "content": "时刻处于纠结当中!!?", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211309tDx3PVejqWgAcRy0.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262058}, {"id": 15890, "content": "12:10睡还是不睡？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237852}, {"id": 16147, "content": "大红唇还是珊瑚粉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241606}, {"id": 16148, "content": "每次打开视频网站，是看这个还是看那个？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241597}, {"id": 17941, "content": "吃什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225391}, {"id": 15894, "content": "说的好像我有钱选似的..???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233467}, {"id": 16918, "content": "购物车里的东西，拿进去放出来，再拿进去再放出来……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215202}, {"id": 20247, "content": "两个女人之间，选择恐惧症", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250265}, {"id": 16664, "content": "早饭吃什么，午饭吃什么，晚饭吃什么。常常想着早饭吃什么想着想着就到了午饭吃什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234048}, {"id": 16153, "content": "今天穿什么衣服呀？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241704}, {"id": 19225, "content": "“对不起，我错了”“没用，晚了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263459}, {"id": 189977, "content": "要不要离婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999408}, {"id": 16410, "content": "就是穷，有钱哪有选择恐惧症！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245288}, {"id": 15900, "content": "一模一样的东西会挑选多次看好坏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238337}, {"id": 15902, "content": "买 还是 买？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211058}, {"id": 17439, "content": "买烟的时候看10~20的都抽遍了，看20~30的没什么喜欢的，看40~50的想买，又想这可能买好几包10~20的呀…… ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 111050}, {"id": 16672, "content": "我喜欢的那件衣服最漂亮 还是妈妈挑的 还是朋友推荐的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248441}, {"id": 20768, "content": "吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272169}, {"id": 15905, "content": "我是天秤座……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238509}, {"id": 15907, "content": "不确定自己是否能成功 试试看吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146452}, {"id": 17956, "content": "每次点单就用石头剪刀布决定", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229103}, {"id": 15909, "content": "股票。买那个或现在该不该卖了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201879}, {"id": 16165, "content": "到底带不带这件件衣服去学校？纠结很久", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241956}, {"id": 15910, "content": "绘图恐惧症", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238631}, {"id": 16168, "content": "哈哈哈没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241978}, {"id": 16169, "content": "适合的和合适的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228673}, {"id": 18729, "content": "吃还是不吃 睡还是不睡 买还是不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135849}, {"id": 15916, "content": "万一再打一把排位赛赢了呢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234474}, {"id": 15661, "content": "选择报考的学校…后来发现能有得上就不错了=_=", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224007}, {"id": 15662, "content": "便利店买饮料", "image": null, "praise_count": 135, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218405}, {"id": 16174, "content": "买东西～买哪些～买这件还是那件？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242062}, {"id": 15663, "content": "每个都想赞，怎么办?", "image": null, "praise_count": 168, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 175156}]}